---
title: Quick Bacon, Mushroom & Truffle Fusilli with Parmesan & Garden Salad
description: Golden ropes of fusilli coated in a creamy mushroom and truffle sauce and sizzled pieces of bacon. Finished with a scattering of sharp Parmesan cheese and a complementary salad, this is nothing short of a small bite of heaven.

